Q 20 : which is better way to create a thread by extending thread class or by implementing runnable interface?
Ans :Implementing Runnable is better because it allows you to extend another class if needed(loosely coupled), 
promoting flexibility. Extending Thread ties you to that class(tightly coupled), limiting inheritance options.
